{"tid":1058113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六旬姑丈藉詞為妙齡姪女按摩　拉下對方內褲非禮　官斥卑劣囚1年","createTime":"2019-03-12T10:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T11:15:19.000Z","uid":8171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"712c91d7cdd962d1c41bbfc94811df9c7364dcc1","tid":1058113,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2540675/org/0d91fdef9483c7ddb3d2c3a859e7b43b.jpg/LaHNhCmpY5aVCliHjWAtstshb2SsaHEpbE4z72xOM-8?v=w800r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2540675%2Forg%2F0d91fdef9483c7ddb3d2c3a859e7b43b.jpg%2FLaHNhCmpY5aVCliHjWAtstshb2SsaHEpbE4z72xOM-8%3Fv%3Dw800r16_9&h=642592a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n六旬姑丈得悉21歲姪女肚痛並獨自在家中休息，即上門探望，並藉詞為對方按摩，卻乘機大肆非禮，不但拉下姪女內褲，又趁機摸及吻她胸部，姪女嘗試把他推開不果，被辱約10分鐘才告結束。姑丈早前在屯門法院承認非禮，求情時稱一時衝動，裁判官今（12日）判刑時指，姑丈以長輩身份非禮姪女，行為卑劣，判他入獄一年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2540185/org/523d963c5fad50021ae1c6c50771b02f.jpg/u_1tV8iu-A5AOzeZE-gXvmPDoD0naqRRe7dxcHu3cXA?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2540185%2Forg%2F523d963c5fad50021ae1c6c50771b02f.jpg%2Fu_1tV8iu-A5AOzeZE-gXvmPDoD0naqRRe7dxcHu3cXA%3Fv%3Dw800&h=a08f23da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年67歲被告，承認一項非禮罪，指他於去年11月在屯門一單位內非禮21歲的女事主。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">官指被告沒考慮事主感受</span><br />\n<br />\n裁判官在判刑時指，被告明知事主只是獨自在家，上門造訪時藉詞幫她按摩腹部，乘機拉起她的上衣，又拉下她的內褲，繼而摸及吻她胸和下體，直言案情嚴重，而事主已多次想把被告推開，但被告不理，繼續其非禮行為，事件長達10分鐘，可見被告既沒有考慮女事主感受，亦用上一定武力。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">被告作為長輩未有尊重女事主</span><br />\n<br />\n裁判官續指，被告作為女事主的姑丈，是她的長輩，卻不尊重對方，事件有違反誠信之嫌，唯一可接受的求情是被告認罪，免事主出庭作證，但認為事件對女事主做成一定傷害，故要作阻嚇性懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">事主曾一度放棄追究</span><br />\n<br />\n案情指，事主當日因為腹痛，獨自在家休息。被告得知後上門造訪，並稱可以替她按摩，惟被告卻趁機扯開事主衣服及內褲，並摸事主胸及下體等，事主感驚慌，曾推開被告，但被告不理，至約10分鐘後才停手及離開。<br />\n<br />\n事主事後向父親哭訴，被告亦有致電事主父道歉，並承認所作的行為。事主有報警，但一度想給被告機會而不作追究，惟來她感到傷心及沮喪，且情緒低落，最後再次報警。被告被捕後承認衝動而犯案。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC406/2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://68.media.tumblr.com/969f252235e407effeaef9f983774187/tumblr_opd2c3Jd4E1wof5i3o1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2F969f252235e407effeaef9f983774187%2Ftumblr_opd2c3Jd4E1wof5i3o1_400.gif&h=ed8a0e8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9be018c4c5fe287e232aac348e3efd9e163c682e","tid":1058113,"uid":8171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://68.media.tumblr.com/031de874be7c5ab604ddd7af754f9ad1/tumblr_opd1nvcTB81wof5i3o1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2F031de874be7c5ab604ddd7af754f9ad1%2Ftumblr_opd1nvcTB81wof5i3o1_400.gif&h=b3d416f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ea47f7ba300c89b4cbaba471d72fff1c7c20d77","tid":1058113,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9be018c4c5fe287e232aac348e3efd9e163c682e","tid":1058113,"uid":8171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://68.media.tumblr.com/031de874be7c5ab604ddd7af754f9ad1/tumblr_opd1nvcTB81wof5i3o1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2F031de874be7c5ab604ddd7af754f9ad1%2Ftumblr_opd1nvcTB81wof5i3o1_400.gif&h=b3d416f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:15:19.000Z","msg":"有無code"}]}